Dr. '''Franz Kalckhoff''' (30 November 1860 – 13 February 1955) was a German [[philatelist]] who signed the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 1934.<ref>''[http://www.abps.org.uk/Awards/Roll_of_Distinguished_Philatelists/RDP_Background_20111231_LR.pdf Background notes on The Roll of Distinguished Philatelists September 2011]'', Roll of Distinguished Philatelists Trust, London, 2011. [https://www.webcitation.org/6OlHSBOTl Archived here.]</ref> He is noted as philatelic author, editor and expert on [[postal stationary]].

